{"tid":1534281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭錄音係咪緊要過新屋嶺集中營？！","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T06:43:25.000Z","uid":1424,"like":174,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"2957f3cacec5290b9029438700e2ebc4f0418b55","tid":1534281,"uid":1424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:07:49.000Z","msg":"你地係咪覺得林鄭係錄音入面喊好慘？<br />\n咁你地記唔記得仲有好多女義士係新屋嶺﹑狗屋﹑狗車俾班狗羞辱，喊得仲悽厲呀？！<br />\n<br />\n你地係咪覺得林鄭去食個飯都俾人錄音好無私隱？<br />\n咁你地記唔記得仲有好多義士，男好女好，係狗屋屙尿都俾班狗睇住呀？！<br />\n<br />\n你地係咪覺得林鄭連辭職都做唔到，係身不由己？<br />\n咁你地記唔記得佢一家都有外國護照，有咩事拍拍羅友就可以走，而好多義士同埋你，都係無得走，今次一輸就慘過死呀？！<br />\n<br />\n記得以上三點既，就唔好再俾人帶風向，唔好再去討論段錄音<br />\n即刻出去推番d 行動post 上黎啦！"},{"pid":"f5565ce52b80acd40366ee82b25d5f16df5f55d9","tid":1534281,"uid":123991,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37657df189d2ab8ec6afbbad0dafd909068b3068","tid":1534281,"uid":293698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:08:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3c1da2bf13e6f6e51dac560a9e95201b5cea7be","tid":1534281,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5caac237a703d38d53578731c70280f82e191abd","tid":1534281,"uid":98926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8/9去美國領事館請願</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">派人道支援/過人權法</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3i9E9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: